    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027260/extras/67fa663a92d9492f82672171e36959ef.avif?t=1763056686\" width=600 height=120 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Behemoth 街机风华丽新作带你左躲右闪，振翅高飞！化身鸡长，带小鸡回鸡窝团圆，并努力收集玉米糖！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027260/extras/5349c7d235fbf664d93273c8013eebce.poster.avif?t=1763056686\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027260/extras/5349c7d235fbf664d93273c8013eebce.webm?t=1763056686\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027260/extras/5349c7d235fbf664d93273c8013eebce.mp4?t=1763056686\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027260/extras/7517c74066c0f677c4db98d0ad795316.avif?t=1763056686\" width=600 height=120 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027260/extras/bcd239b5a98455856d7ea7fcf01032ed.webp?t=1763056686\" width=16 height=16 /></span> 翱翔天际，找齐雏鸡后带回鸡窝，提高分数！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027260/extras/bcd239b5a98455856d7ea7fcf01032ed.webp?t=1763056686\" width=16 height=16 /></span> 努力收集玉米糖，解锁包括鸡体颜色、喙部、肉垂、鸡脚等大量新造型吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027260/extras/bcd239b5a98455856d7ea7fcf01032ed.webp?t=1763056686\" width=16 height=16 /></span> 利用强大的强化道具让旅程更顺遂</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027260/extras/bcd239b5a98455856d7ea7fcf01032ed.webp?t=1763056686\" width=16 height=16 /></span> 在每日排行榜上一较高下，比谁分数最高和通过的检查点数量最多</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027260/extras/bcd239b5a98455856d7ea7fcf01032ed.webp?t=1763056686\" width=16 height=16 /></span> 帮鸡长精心打扮，可爱风还是可怖风任你选……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027260/extras/bcd239b5a98455856d7ea7fcf01032ed.webp?t=1763056686\" width=16 height=16 /></span> 把握鸡生不容错过的鸡彩欢乐*</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >          <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027260/extras/c927496394eee40e4e5f7f43ada2048f.webp?t=1763056686\" width=16 height=16 /></span> <i>*前提是期望不要过高（鸡的平均寿命为 5-7 年）</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027260/extras/8f4b4a96083f89ce24faa2f63549059a.poster.avif?t=1763056686\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027260/extras/8f4b4a96083f89ce24faa2f63549059a.webm?t=1763056686\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027260/extras/8f4b4a96083f89ce24faa2f63549059a.mp4?t=1763056686\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
